<p style="text-align: center;">
	<br>
</p>

<p><strong><u>Bước 3:</u></strong> Lựa chọn dữ liệu muốn khôi phục</p>

<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://support.cloudpro.vn/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1566461353698.png" style="width: 720px; border: 1px solid rgb(176, 170, 170);" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-result="success"></p>

